reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Hilarious and useful
reviews.reviewText: Got these as a Christmas present and laughed out loud. For context, I’m an exhausted college student and definitely need to outsource my f…s.The words come out of the jar and are all wooden and cut quite well. I didn’t notice any glaring issues in production.I loved them and think they’re a great white elephant gift or a fantastic gift for a friend that would appreciate this humor.
